Hello I am Elizabeth Tudor, Fujiwara, Reilly, Windsor, York, Of Cleve's. This is me: [[File:Bongo figure-British Museum (2).jpg|Bongo_figure-British_Museum_(2)]] Yes yes I know I'm stunning. 🫰
== Time in the army == It was absolutely appalling. The army commander sir Johnson, Amaterasu, hehrhehharf, was my commander. Me in the military: [[File:Toy soldier (AM 1996.165.18-2).jpg|Toy_soldier_(AM_1996.165.18-2)]] Ruuuuule Britannia == War == War was tough thou shalt not need to imagine it. This was a photo: [[File:British Museum 18.jpg|British_Museum_18]] I fought along side Emperor kanmu to defeat south Africa and won. == British == British. == Final == This is it for the Wikipedia page. Have a good rest of the day. Rule Meeeeeeee.
